{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"行内元素","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"摘要","isH3":false,"content":"<p>HTML (超文本标记语言) 元素大多数都是行内元素或<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements\">块级元素</a>。一个行内元素只占据它对应标签的边框所包含的空间。下面这个例子说明了行内元素的作用范围：</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"inline_example","title":"行内元素示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>This <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>span<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> is an inline element; its background has been colored to display both the beginning and end of the inline element's influence<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">span</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #8ABB55<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Inline example sample\" id=\"frame_inline_example\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements/_sample_.inline_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"行内元素与块级元素对比","title":"行内元素与块级元素对比","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"内容\">内容</dt>\n <dd>一般情况下，行内元素只能包含数据和其他行内元素。</dd>\n <dd>而块级元素可以包含行内元素和其他块级元素。这种结构上的包含继承区别可以使块级元素创建比行内元素更”大型“的结构。</dd>\n <dt id=\"格式\">格式</dt>\n <dd>默认情况下，行内元素不会以新行开始，而块级元素会新起一行。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"elements","title":"行内元素列表","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的元素都是行内元素：</p>\n\n<ul id=\"inline-elements\">\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/b\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/b\">b</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/big\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/big\">big</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/i\">i</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/small\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/small\">small</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/tt\">tt</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/abbr\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/abbr\">abbr</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/acronym\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/acronym\">acronym</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/cite\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/cite\">cite</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/code\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/code\">code</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dfn\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/dfn\">dfn</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/em\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/em\">em</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/kbd\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/kbd\">kbd</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/strong\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/strong\">strong</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/samp\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/samp\">samp</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/var\">var</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/a\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/a\">a</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/bdo\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/bdo\">bdo</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/br\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/br\">br</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/Img\">img</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/map\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/map\">map</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/object\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/object\">object</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/q\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/q\">q</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/script\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/Script\">script</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/span\">span</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sub\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/sub\">sub</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/sup\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/sup\">sup</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/button\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/button\">button</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/Input\">input</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/label\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/label\">label</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/select\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/select\">select</a>, <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/textarea\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Element/textarea\">textarea</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"另请参阅","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements\" title=\"zh-CN/HTML/Block-level_elements\">块级元素</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"摘要","id":"summary"},{"text":"行内元素示例","id":"inline_example"},{"text":"行内元素与块级元素对比","id":"行内元素与块级元素对比"},{"text":"行内元素列表","id":"elements"},{"text":"另请参阅","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"HTML (超文本标记语言) 元素大多数都是行内元素或块级元素。一个行内元素只占据它对应标签的边框所包含的空间。下面这个例子说明了行内元素的作用范围：","popularity":0.0009,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Inline-Elemente","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"